{
  "stem": "27747.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She-- very possible that we would have been able to-- to evacuate with them, but I don't think my mother wanted to go to Russia, to the Soviet Union, I would call it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The very first thing was the Germans bombed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did not bomb the outskirts of Hoszcza, only the town of Hoszcza.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our home was burned, many other homes were burned, and there were a lot of casualties.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they were alive, they were wounded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother and I and my sister, we hid in the-- in the-- you know, the weed was high already and that's where we hid.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the bombs were all around, with exploding all around us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- the people said that the reason they did not bomb the villages is because the Germans pointed out-- the Ukrainians and the Germans pointed out where the Jewish people lived.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is why Hoszcza suffered such casualties.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And their homes were spared and so where their lives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we all wore-- yes, men, women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- since I was 17, I, too, wore a star.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '42. '42.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We could not live on the outskirts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We worried very much the Ukrainians would harm us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were collaborators hand in hand with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- that's why we moved to that pharmacy, which were my cousins pharmacy, although my uncle wasn't alive anymore, but she, his daughter, was a pharmacist and so was her husband.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were very lenient with him, the Germans and the Ukrainians, because it was the only pharmacy in the area and they were very, very capable people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had a room there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
